What is Spread Operator?

Spread operator is used to expand values from arrays or objects.

Arrays
let arr1 = [1, 2, 3];
let arr2 = [...arr1];

console.log(arr2);
Merge Arrays
let a = [1, 2];
let b = [3, 4];

let result = [...a, ...b];

console.log(result);
Objects
let student = {
    name: "Atharv",
    age: 19
};

let newStudent = {
    ...student,
    city: "Pune"
};

console.log(newStudent);
Key Takeaways
Copies data safely
Combines arrays/objects
Very important in React
